          300KB max. Lazy load images below fold (Framer does this automatically).
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <span class="font-bold">Animation optimization:</span> Fewer simultaneous animations = better
          performance. Limit scroll-triggered animations to 5-10 per page. Use transforms and
